  			<div id="item-1834"><p>I can&#8217;t believe that chicken leg-thigh combinations will cook in 15 minutes.  Does this sound right?</p></div>
  			<div class="date byline">
  				
  				<span><span class="alias">Aunt Sue</span></span>
  				<span>on April 10, 2006</span>
  			</div>
  		</div><div>
  			<div id="item-1835"><p>Leland, I&#8217;m so glad you liked this so much! Aunt Sue &#8211; the roasting time is 15 minutes, but you take additional time to properly brown each side of the chicken.</p></div>
  			<div class="date byline">
  				
